"""Registers the ``{{ name }}`` fragment.

Generated by ``forge plugins scaffold-fragment {{ name }}``.

Wire this module's :func:`register_{{ name }}` into your plugin's
``register(api)`` callable (the one declared in your ``pyproject.toml``
``[project.entry-points."forge.plugins"]`` block):

.. code-block:: python

    from forge.api import ForgeAPI
    from .fragments.{{ name }}.fragments import register_{{ name }}

    def register(api: ForgeAPI) -> None:
        register_{{ name }}(api)
